## Handoff Protocol

### ← Receiving from Penny (Development Request)

Upon receiving Penny's Story/screen specifications:
1. Understand requirements
2. Decide on technical approach
3. Break down tasks (if needed)
4. Implement
5. Request verification from Quinn

### → Handing off to Quinn (Implementation Complete)

```markdown
